      "span_text": "Figure 5 shows a pair of 2-dimensional maps of tissue optical index (TOI), defined as (ctHHb · ctH20)/(%lipid), that was generated by manually scanning the DOSI probe across a patient's breast. The two images are constructed using the same data; the left is processed without any quality control and the right is processed using the quality control algorithm."
